  // through interactWardstone() — it branches by flag inside. Previously this
  // dispatch only checked `isWardstone`, which silently broke marsh lanterns,
  // the cathedral bell, crypt lanterns, talent shrines, the bridge edge, the
  // vow stone, the trial anvil, the pact stone, and the new sacrifice altars.
  // Any object that's been pushed onto state.wardstones with one of these
  // flags is now routed correctly.
