// SHOP_ITEMS is the registry of buyables shown between waves. Each item:
//   id        — stable string for deduping one-time purchases via state.shopBought
//   name/desc — display text in the panel
//   cost      — gold price, NEVER scales (per the design spec — costs are flat)
//   once      — true means item disappears after one buy (e.g. unique upgrades)
//   canBuy()  — optional gating beyond gold + once. Returns false if unbuyable
//               for non-gold reasons (missing prerequisite companion etc).
//   buy()     — the effect. Modifies state / cfg / spawns companion etc.
